### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Successful Payment (Test Card)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/stripe/transaction
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 2000,
  "currency": "usd",
  "paymentMethodId": "pm_card_visa",
  "description": "Test payment - Visa",
  "customerEmail": "success@example.com",
  "metadata": {
    "orderId": "12345",
    "environment": "test"
  }
}

